keyboard shortcuts
==================
	control + command + shift + /  	=> function tooltip
	control + command + left      	=> jump back
	control + command + right       => jump forward
	shift + command + f             => find navigator
	command + f  			=> search
	option + command + enter        => swift ui preview
	command + shift + j 		=> reveal in project navigator
	command + shift + o		=> open quickly

with mouse
=========
	command + click                 => function definition
	option + click 			=> function tooltip

